Package: rnirs
Type: Package
Title: Locally Weighted PLS Regression and Discrimination
Version: 1.3-6
Author: Matthieu Lesnoff <matthieu.lesnoff@cirad.fr>
Maintainer: Matthieu Lesnoff <matthieu.lesnoff@cirad.fr>
Description: Statistical tool box for locally weighted prediction
  methods: regression for quantitative responses and discrimination for qualitative responses. 
  The prediction models can use partial least squares dimension reductions or other methods.
  The package was primarily dedicated to near infrared spectral data 
  but is generic for many other types of data.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports:  data.table, FNN, ggplot2, gridExtra, ptw, scales, signal 
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
URL: https://github.com/mlesnoff/rnirs
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: yes
